- Auto-detects and adapts UI for newly connected GPUs

## Idle Detection System (Importance: 75)
- Advanced GPU idle detection logic:
  - Monitors utilization across all detected GPUs
  - Triggers alerts when usage drops below 30% threshold
  - Accumulates idle time with 5-minute notification threshold
  - Implements reset logic when GPU becomes active
- System tray integration provides persistent monitoring

